data.description: Fabulous Condominium sitting on Allenmore Golf Course #18 Hole.  Mt. Rainier view from the large private deck. No stairs inside your unit - all 1 level and a fantastic layout!  Gated entry off South Cedar St., to your private parking garage.  Elevator & 2 sources of stair access to unit on the 2nd floor.  This location is truly CENTAL to all Tacoma has to offer. The hallways and rooms accommodate accessibility for motorized scooters or wheelchairs.
